nodes.title: Final prompt preview
widgets_values: The video shows a female knight standing in an archway, holding a sword in her right hand. She has long blonde hair and is wearing full metal armor, including breastplates, gauntlets, and a cloak. The background is dark and Gothic-style, with columns and arches. The lighting is dramatic, casting shadows on her figure. The video is in black and white, with a high resolution and a realistic style. The knight has a serious expression and is positioned in the center of the video.shaking her ass, natural motion and jiggle.

If you leave either WIDTH or HEIGHT at 0 and specify only one, it maintains the aspect ratio and no cropping.

If you specify both it will crop it.
Picks last frame and saves it.
Delete Patch Sage Attention KJ if you don't have sage attention installed.
Using positive only might give more motion, i still need to test it more.
